results.title: Shiver Part Two
results.description: The Suit arrives and begins his search for Venom; Patricia and her army companions try to determine what went wrong at the civilian arctic base and Perry, the lone survivor, isn't long on answers; Strange things begin to happen at the army base culminating in the Venom alien coming out to play.

results.title: Shiver Part Three
results.description: The Suit shows up at the army base and tries to take down Venom while keeping the troops informed and in line; Things don't work out exactly as planned.

results.title: Shiver Part Four
results.description: The Suit is down; Venom picks off all of the Army officers and comes after Patricia; Perry tells Patricia that the Venom Alien is an alien experiment gone wild.
